definitions.definition: A seat or chair on wheels , pushed by somebody walking behind it, typically used for transporting babies and young children .
Men's semiformal daytime dress comprising a grey or black single- or double-breasted coat , grey striped or checked formal trousers , a grey or silver necktie , and a grey, black or buff waistcoat .

main_definition: ( US , Canada , Australia ) A seat or chair on wheels , pushed by somebody walking behind it, typically used for transporting babies and young children .
